#strap
  %p Report and view problems in hospitals

#step_feedprob
  #problems
    %h2 Report a Problem
    %p 
      This site is for reporting specific problems in hospitals, like broken equipment or 
      badly cleaned areas.
    %p 
      Your comments will be emailed to the hospital, so that they can take action to fix 
      the problem
    %p.button
      %a{:href => '/report'} Report a Problem
  
  #feedback
    %h2 Give Feedback
    %p
      If you want to provide general feedback on the care you received, you should visit 
      <a href="http://www.patientopinion.org.uk">Patient Opinion</a>. 
    %p
      This site is only for reporting specific problems.
    %p.button
      %a{:href => 'http://www.patientopinion.org.uk'} Give Feedback

  %div.clear


